article.description: — Dawson Garcia tied his season high with 20 points as Marquette topped Providence 79-69 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Garcia scores 20 to lead Marquette past Providence 79-69
article.linkText: Garcia scores 20 to lead Marquette past Providence 79-69
article.story: MILWAUKEE -- — Dawson Garcia tied his season high with 20 points as Marquette topped Providence 79-69 on Tuesday night. Koby McEwen had 17 points, eight rebounds and six assists for Marquette (7-6, 3-4 Big East Conference). D.J. Carton added 13 points. Jamal Cain had 12 points. Nate Watson had 18 points for the Friars (7-6, 3-4). David Duke added 17 points and nine assists. A.J. Reeves had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25
